### 📦 Assets – Neues Asset anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "TEST",
  "name": "Test Asset",
  "assetType": "CRYPTO"
}

### 💰 Preise – Mock-Refresh aller Preise
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prices/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

### 💹 Transaktionen – Kauf mit PFG-Fragen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/txns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTC",
  "timestamp": "2025-10-22T18:00:00",
  "side": "BUY",
  "quantity": 0.005,
  "price": 65000.00,
  "note": "Testkauf über REST Client",
  "pfg": [3, 4, 3, 4, 3]
}

### 😃 Emotion Log – Stimmung erfassen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/emotions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "day": "2025-10-22",
  "mood": 4,
  "note": "Super produktiver Tag!"
}
